        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Protecting Our Local Elections Act or the POLE Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill prohibits a state from receiving federal election administration funds if the state does not permit localities to hold elections for local office in odd-numbered years.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
